title: Shark Tank Season 8
description:
Because Pirate Bay perpetually indicated zero seeders and leechers (erroneously) in my previous version of this torrent, I decided to delete that previous version and re-launch it as this identical torrent.

Shark Tank is an American reality television series that premiered August 9, 2009 on ABC. Based on the worldwide television series format Dragons' Den that originally aired in Japan, Shark Tank has aspiring entrepreneurs make business presentations to a panel of potential investors, the so-called "sharks". Enjoy!!
